    Phoenix Suns

    Basketball Team

    All images

    An American professional basketball team based in Phoenix, Arizona. The Suns compete in the National Basketball Association (NBA), as a member of the league's Western Conference Pacific Division.

    nba.com
    Coach

    Location

    League

    Division

    Owner
    Robert Sarver

    The Suns play their home games at the 'Phoenix Suns Arena'.

    The franchise began play in 1968 as an expansion team.

    The Suns are the only team in their division not based in California.
